---
title: Baja-Style Blackened Prawns with Garlic Rice & Aioli Walnut Slaw
description: There’s a hint of smokiness in the air and it’s coming from these prawns, the All-American mild spice does wonders
when cooked into prawns and served on top of a bed of rice. Not to mention, the smokey aioli tossed through the
slaw. It’s a firestorm of flavour tonight!
